ZH: 我下个月就要回国了。
EN: I will return to my country next month.

ZH: 你什么时候回国？
EN: When will you go back to your country?

ZH: 我想明年暑假回国看看家人。
EN: I want to go back to my country next summer vacation to visit my family.

ZH: 这次回国是为了参加毕业典礼。
EN: I am going back to my country this time to attend the graduation ceremony.

ZH: 他回国后马上就要开始新工作。
EN: He will start a new job immediately after returning to his country.

ZH: 我的家乡在回国的路上。
EN: My hometown is on the way back to my country.

ZH: 因为疫情，我不得不提前回国。
EN: Because of the pandemic, I have to return to my country earlier.

ZH: 回国旅行需要提前准备好护照和签证。
EN: Returning to the country for a trip requires preparing your passport and visa in advance.

ZH: 我们准备好了回国的礼物。
EN: We have prepared gifts for our return to the country.

ZH: 在机场送别了我们的朋友，然后开始回国的旅程。
EN: We bid farewell to our friend at the airport, and then began our journey back to the country.

ZH: 这次回国是为了处理一些家庭事务。
EN: I am going back to my country this time to take care of some family matters.

ZH: 我父母很期待我的回国。
EN: My parents are looking forward to my return to the country.

ZH: 回国过年是中国人的传统习俗。
EN: Going back to the country for Chinese New Year is a traditional custom for Chinese people.

ZH: 我的朋友打算暑假回国实习。
EN: My friend plans to go back to the country for an internship during the summer vacation.

ZH: 我需要买张机票才能回国。
EN: I need to buy a plane ticket to return to my country.

ZH: 回国的路上，我遇到了一位老朋友。
EN: On the way back to the country, I met an old friend.

ZH: 他经常回国出差。
EN: He often travels back to his country for business trips.

ZH: 回国后我打算开始学习汉语。
EN: After returning to my country, I plan to start learning Chinese.

ZH: 我希望能够顺利回国。
EN: I hope to be able to return to my country smoothly.

ZH: 回国的时候，我想去游览一些名胜古迹。
